@host = http://localhost:5204

### 📋 List all available endpoints
GET {{host}}/
Accept: application/json

### ❌ Scenario 1: Invalid registration — duplicate username/email + password contains username
POST {{host}}/api/register/invalid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "adminPass"
}

### ❌ Scenario 2: Invalid event — reserved title + New Year's Day conflict + bad date range
POST {{host}}/api/event/invalid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Event",
  "startDate": "2027-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-12-31",
  "delay": 100
}

### ❌ Scenario 3: Invalid order — unknown product + total exceeds async/sync limits
POST {{host}}/api/order/invalid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Unknown",
  "quantity": 1000,
  "unitPrice": 120,
  "delay": 100
}
